.detail-row--lowest   { }  // no background; just the green dot in the Price cell
.detail-row--declined { opacity: 0.6; }
.detail-row--requote  { }  // orange Price cell (existing .price-requested-cell updated above)
```

**Barbell action bar** (existing HTML in `detail-cell-renderer.component.html`):
```scss
