```
**[component SCSS]** for the detail renderer.

---

## 6 · View / layout persistence

| What | How |
|---|---|
| Frozen identity columns (Price Code · Pic · Desc) | Update the "Default" GridLayout record on the backend to include pinned state. Also call `applyColumnState` on `firstDataRendered` (see §5d) to backfill existing saved views without breaking them. |
| Density preference | `localStorage.setItem('rfq:density', d)` — no backend needed. |
| Scenario group open/closed | AG Grid saves column group state as part of column state in the GridLayout. The existing `onSaveLayout` already captures it — no extra work. |
| Toolbar density toggle | Read from `localStorage` in `ngOnInit`; apply in `gridReady`. |

---

